=== Designated Cultural Properties ===
=== Nationally Designated Natural Monument ===
* Great Cedar of Oyama (National {{ill|lt=Natural Monument|Q23790|WD=Q23790|1=Natural monument}})<ref>{{Cite web|Japanese|date= |url=http://www.pref.gifu.lg.jp/kyoiku/bunka/bunkazai/17768/tennen/ooyama.html |title=Great Cedar of Oyama |publisher=Gifu Prefecture |accessdate=2017-09-17}}</ref>
On the right side of the worship hall, midway up the stone steps leading to the main hall, stands a giant cedar designated as a National Natural Monument, said to be over 1,200 years old, with a circumference of 8.9 m and a height of 36 m.

Because the area around the shrine forms a well-preserved green space mainly consisting of {{ill|lt=Japanese cedar|Q147388|WD=Q147388|1=Cryptomeria}} and {{ill|lt=Japanese cypress|Q917187|WD=Q917187|1=Chamaecyparis obtusa}},

it was designated as a Green Environment Conservation Area on November 6, {{ill|lt=1984|Q2432|WD=Q2432|1=1984}} (Shōwa 59)<ref>{{Cite web|Japanese|url=https://www.pref.gifu.lg.jp/page/6062.html|title=List of Green Environment Conservation Areas|publisher=Gifu Prefecture|date=|accessdate=2024-10-20}}</ref>.

